{"tid":21933,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲試過上司將你同單身既同事湊做一對","createTime":"2016-12-04T06:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T09:37:13.000Z","uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"834714b5faee37e8d8963bb1fa84539b4b6b5501","tid":21933,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早幾個月部門黎左個新黎既女仔，細我兩年，乜都唔識全部由我教<br />\n而個女仔因為做左陣廢青同d朋友斷絕曬關係，而且老豆走左佬，身邊得我一個男性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁個女仔係好乖好純既，但係純到蠢左D囉<br />\n老細將自己既公事同私事都叫佢用手提打比我，佢打完都唔知點解，過兩日先黎問我點解要用佢手提打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw有心上人，但係老細唔支持我鍾意個心上人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce06a637a6399751aa2107026a40a3512565f493","tid":21933,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"關你老細撚事咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7085b09cc1e52483bed7821788477a6dffb3d114","tid":21933,"uid":36315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"你up乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d15389a402cf49668b9dee7d4bb605ba7e7e2a","tid":21933,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"你老細係你老母？"},{"pid":"35d379d3ac1d26fcb17d053efd2eb1cf856d7665","tid":21933,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你老細撚事咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔是囉，條粉皮下下叫我送條女返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明lunch time係分開放，要我專登同佢一齊放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402aba3746d5d179746022e4d9d7bd23887dc699","tid":21933,"uid":50605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07: